nt bosses, but dont forget the beer!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/33eb573952c468f446d1dfa2c28da363.poster.avif?t=1591053749\" width=358 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/33eb573952c468f446d1dfa2c28da363.webm?t=1591053749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/33eb573952c468f446d1dfa2c28da363.mp4?t=1591053749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• 20 levels with 3 sub quests each<br><br>• 5 customization options with more than 4 items each.<br><br>• Cool weapons.<br><br>• Great feel on controls.<br><br>• Awesome steam cards !<br><br>• 8 Bosses that will put your skills to proof.<br><br>• Great OST that will really catch you.<br><br>• Cool grenades to burn them all !<br><br>• Available in 3 different languages: english, brazilian portuguese and french.<br><br>You can also customize your character on different aspects, hair, glasses, clothes, helmets and even skin color. All while listening to some great music to level up your bad ass instincts. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/eadda772ee4d4f366097bc8c135926fb.poster.avif?t=1591053749\" width=358 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/eadda772ee4d4f366097bc8c135926fb.webm?t=1591053749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869030/extras/eadda772ee4d4f366097bc8c135926fb.mp4?t=1591053749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
